  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Chemistry
Topic:   Conservation of Mass
Formula: Reactants mass = Products mass
Note:    Mass is conserved in all chemical reactions

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Wave Equation
Formula: v = fλ
Note:    Speed of wave = frequency × wavelength

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   2nd Law of Thermodynamics
Formula: ΔS ≥ 0
Note:    Entropy always increases in isolated systems

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   Cell Theory
Formula: All life is made of cells arising from pre-existing cells
Note:    Foundation of modern biology

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Euler's Identity
Formula: e^(iπ) + 1 = 0
Note:    Relates five fundamental constants; called most beautiful equation

